---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout>
	<div class="overflow-x-hidden">

		<div class="relative isolate px-6 pt-14 lg:px-8">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl pt-16 pb-16 sm:pt-24 sm:pb-20 lg:pt-32 lg:pb-20">
				<div class="text-center">
					<h2 class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-brand">Hi, I'm Val Diaz — Lead Product Designer</h2>
					<h1 class="text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-balance text-gray-900 sm:text-7xl">Engineering
						Logic. Visual Mastery. Lead Mindset.</h1>
					<p class="mt-8 text-lg font-medium text-pretty text-gray-500 sm:text-xl/8">I design scalable systems
						and high-impact digital products. From auditing Figma libraries to leading multidisciplinary
						teams, I ensure every pixel and interface serves a purpose and every system is built to last.
					</p>
					<p class="mt-8 text-lg font-medium text-pretty text-gray-500 sm:text-xl/8">Currently leading design
						excellence at EPAM for global brands.</p>
					<div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6">
						<a href="/casos"
							class="rounded-full bg-brand px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition-colors hover:bg-brand-hover">View
							Projects</a>
						<a href="/sobre-mi" class="text-sm/6 font-semibold text-gray-900">Learn more about me <span
								aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="relative isolate px-6 pt-12 pb-24 sm:pt-16 sm:pb-32 lg:px-8">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
				<h2 class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-brand">How do I work</h2>
				<p class="mt-2 text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-balance text-gray-900 sm:text-6xl">My Core
					Pillars</p>
			</div>
			<p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-center text-lg font-medium text-pretty text-gray-600 sm:text-xl/8">
				Driving product success by bridging the gap between design and engineering through robust systems,
				strategic thinking, and collaborative leadership.</p>

			<div
				class="mx-auto mt-16 grid max-w-lg grid-cols-1 items-stretch gap-6 sm:mt-20 lg:max-w-4xl lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-8">
				<div class="rounded-3xl bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-md p-8 shadow-xl ring-1 ring-white/60 sm:p-10">
					<h3 class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-brand">Scalable Design Systems & Ops</h3>
					<p class="mt-6 text-base/7 text-gray-600">I architect and maintain robust design languages that
						bridge the gap between design and code. From auditing extensive Figma libraries to defining
						global standards, I ensure consistency and efficiency at every scale.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-3xl bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-md p-8 shadow-xl ring-1 ring-white/60 sm:p-10">
					<h3 class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-brand">Engineering-Driven UX Strategy</h3>
					<p class="mt-6 text-base/7 text-gray-600">With a background in Computer Engineering, I approach UX
						with a logic-first mindset. I design high-fidelity solutions that are not only visually premium
						but technically feasible and aligned with business goals.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="rounded-3xl bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-md p-8 shadow-xl ring-1 ring-white/60 sm:p-10">
					<h3 class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-brand">Mentorship & Team Leadership</h3>
					<p class="mt-6 text-base/7 text-gray-600">Leading is about empowering others. I have mentored
						emerging talent and led cross-functional teams, ensuring design quality through rigorous reviews
						and established workflows that foster excellence, including leading design quality for teams of
						up to 5 designers.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="py-24 sm:py-32">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
				<div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:text-center">
					<h2 class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-brand">How I Can Help</h2>
					<p
						class="mt-2 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-pretty text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl lg:text-balance">
						Services</p>
					<p
						class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-center text-lg font-medium text-pretty text-gray-600 sm:text-xl/8">
						Leveraging engineering logic and premium visual craft to solve complex product challenges. I
						help teams scale through robust design systems, strategic leadership, and efficient workflows.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-none">
					<dl class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-10 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-y-16">
						<div class="flex flex-col">
							<dt class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-gray-900">
								<div class="mb-4 flex size-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-brand">
									<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"
										aria-hidden="true" class="size-6 text-white">
										<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
											d="M6.429 9.75 2.25 12l4.179 2.25m0-4.5 5.571 3 5.571-3m-11.142 0L2.25 7.5 12 2.25l9.75 5.25-4.179 2.25m0 0L21.75 12l-4.179 2.25m0 0l4.179 2.25L12 21.75 2.25 16.5l4.179-2.25m11.142 0-5.571 3-5.571-3" />
									</svg>
								</div>
								Design Systems & Scalability
							</dt>
							<dd class="mt-2 text-base/7 text-gray-600">
								<ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
									<li><strong>Audit & Strategy:</strong> I conduct deep inventories of existing Figma
										libraries to identify inconsistencies and technical debt.</li>
									<li><strong>System Architecture:</strong> Building and migrating robust, multi-brand
										design languages that ensure consistency across Web, iOS, and Android.</li>
									<li><strong>Documentation & Handoff:</strong> Creating clear governance and
										workflows that bridge the gap between design and engineering.</li>
								</ul>
							</dd>
						</div>
						<div class="flex flex-col">
							<dt class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-gray-900">
								<div class="mb-4 flex size-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-brand">
									<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"
										aria-hidden="true" class="size-6 text-white">
										<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
											d="M9.813 15.904 9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09 3.09ZM18.259 8.715 18 9.75l-.259-1.035a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-2.455-2.456L14.25 6l1.036-.259a3.375 3.375 0 0 0 2.455-2.456L18 2.25l.259 1.035a3.375 3.375 0 0 0 2.456 2.456L21.75 6l-1.035.259a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-2.456 2.456ZM16.894 20.567 16.5 21.75l-.394-1.183a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-1.423-1.423L13.5 18.75l1.183-.394a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 1.423-1.423l.394-1.183.394 1.183a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 1.423 1.423l1.183.394-1.183.394a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-1.423 1.423Z" />
									</svg>
								</div>
								Strategic Visual & Product Design
							</dt>
							<dd class="mt-2 text-base/7 text-gray-600">
								<ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
									<li><strong>High-Fidelity Craft:</strong> Transforming complex business requirements
										into premium, polished interfaces that align with brand identity.</li>
									<li><strong>Prototyping & Motion:</strong> Using Lottie and advanced
										micro-interactions to enhance user engagement and define motion standards.</li>
									<li><strong>UX/UI Inventory:</strong> Streamlining digital products through
										systematic audits and information architecture improvements.</li>
								</ul>
							</dd>
						</div>
						<div class="flex flex-col">
							<dt class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-gray-900">
								<div class="mb-4 flex size-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-brand">
									<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"
										aria-hidden="true" class="size-6 text-white">
										<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
											d="M15 19.128a9.38 9.38 0 0 0 2.625.372 9.337 9.337 0 0 0 4.121-.952 4.125 4.125 0 0 0-7.533-2.493M15 19.128v-.003c0-1.113-.285-2.16-.786-3.07M15 19.128v.106A12.318 12.318 0 0 1 8.624 21c-2.331 0-4.512-.645-6.374-1.766l-.001-.109a6.375 6.375 0 0 1 11.964-3.07M12 6.375a3.375 3.375 0 1 1-6.75 0 3.375 3.375 0 0 1 6.75 0Zm8.25 2.25a2.625 2.625 0 1 1-5.25 0 2.625 2.625 0 0 1 5.25 0Z" />
									</svg>
								</div>
								Design Ops & Leadership
							</dt>
							<dd class="mt-2 text-base/7 text-gray-600">
								<ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
									<li><strong>Team Governance:</strong> Establishing internal frameworks and best
										practices to improve collaboration and output quality.</li>
									<li><strong>Mentorship:</strong> Guiding designers through career development,
										technical workshops, and rigorous design reviews.</li>
									<li><strong>Stakeholder Management:</strong> Articulating design decisions to
										clients and engineering teams to ensure project alignment and success.</li>
								</ul>
							</dd>
						</div>
					</dl>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		

			<div class="relative isolate py-24 sm:py-32">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
				<h2 class="text-center text-base/7 font-semibold text-brand tracking-wide uppercase">Case studies</h2>
				<p
					class="mx-auto mt-2 max-w-lg text-center text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-balance text-gray-950 sm:text-5xl">
					Turning Complex Challenges into Seamless Experiences</p>

				<div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-8 items-start">

					<div class="lg:col-span-7 group cursor-pointer flex flex-col">
						<div class="overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] w-full h-[300px] sm:h-[450px] mb-8 shadow-sm">
							<img src="/DestinationDecoderExp.svg" alt="App de Travel"
								class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105" />
						</div>
						<div class="flex flex-col items-start px-2">
							<span
								class="rounded-full bg-gray-100 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-bold text-gray-600 mb-4 tracking-wider uppercase">Travel
								& AI</span>
							<h3
								class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-950 mb-4 leading-tight group-hover:text-brand transition-colors">
								Scaling Growth through Motion & Systems</h3>
							<p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6 line-clamp-3">Leading cross-platform experiences for
								web and mobile. Contributed to $14.9M GP and 1.48M installs by surpassing annual targets
								by 148%.</p>
							<span
								class="text-brand font-bold text-base hover:text-brand-hover transition-colors flex items-center gap-1">View
								more <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></span>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col gap-10">

						<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 group cursor-pointer items-start">
							<div class="w-full sm:w-44 sm:h-44 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-sm">
								<img src="/airgas.png"
									alt="Design Systems"
									class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105" />
							</div>
							<div class="flex flex-col items-start justify-center pt-2 sm:pt-0">
								<span
									class="rounded-full bg-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] font-bold text-gray-600 mb-3 tracking-wider uppercase">Gas & Design
									Systems</span>
								<h3
									class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-950 mb-2 leading-tight group-hover:text-brand transition-colors">
									Elevating Design Excellence & Ops</h3>
								<p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4 line-clamp-2">Redesigned, managed and evolved
									complex UI libraries for a Fortune 500 client.</p>
								<span
									class="text-brand font-bold text-sm hover:text-brand-hover transition-colors flex items-center gap-1">View
									more <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></span>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 group cursor-pointer items-start">
							<div class="w-full sm:w-44 sm:h-44 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-sm">
								<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551288049-bebda4e38f71?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop"
									alt="Data"
									class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105" />
							</div>
							<div class="flex flex-col items-start justify-center pt-2 sm:pt-0">
								<span
									class="rounded-full bg-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] font-bold text-gray-600 mb-3 tracking-wider uppercase">Production & Data
									Architecture</span>
								<h3
									class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-950 mb-2 leading-tight group-hover:text-brand transition-colors">
									Revolutionizing Production Planning at Scale</h3>
								<p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4 line-clamp-2">Reduced development time by 20% and increased customer satisfaction by 15% by unifying the UX across platforms and establishing a scalable Design System..</p>
								<span
									class="text-brand font-bold text-sm hover:text-brand-hover transition-colors flex items-center gap-1">View
									more <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></span>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 group cursor-pointer items-start">
							<div
								class="w-full sm:w-44 sm:h-44 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-sm bg-gray-900">
								<img src="/Coign.png" alt="Fintech"
									class="w-full h-full object-cover object-left-top transition-transform duration-700 opacity-90 group-hover:scale-105 group-hover:opacity-100" />
							</div>
							<div class="flex flex-col items-start justify-center pt-2 sm:pt-0">
								<span
									class="rounded-full bg-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] font-bold text-gray-600 mb-3 tracking-wider uppercase">Fintech & Visual Design</span>
								<h3
									class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-950 mb-2 leading-tight group-hover:text-brand transition-colors">
									Architecting an "Unmissable" Experience</h3>
								<p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4 line-clamp-2">Spearheaded a robust Web App that
									unified applicant management, earning praise from The WSJ.</p>
								<span
									class="text-brand font-bold text-sm hover:text-brand-hover transition-colors flex items-center gap-1">View
									more <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></span>
							</div>
						</div>

					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="mt-20 flex justify-center">
					<a href="/casos"
						class="text-brand font-bold text-lg hover:text-brand-hover transition-colors flex items-center gap-2">
						See more case studies <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<section id="testimonials-section" class="relative isolate py-24 sm:py-32">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
				<div class="mb-20 text-center">
					<h2 class="text-center text-base/7 font-semibold text-brand">High-impact feedback from leaders
						across top technology teams</h2>
					<p
						class="mx-auto mt-2 max-w-lg text-center text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-balance text-gray-950 sm:text-5xl">
						What people are saying</p>
					<p
						class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-center text-lg font-medium text-pretty text-gray-600 sm:text-xl/8">
						8+ clients from 4+ countries.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="mt-10 flex flex-col gap-8 w-full">
				<div id="scroll-row-1" class="flex gap-8 w-max will-change-transform items-stretch"
					style="transform: translateX(-15%);">
					<div
						class="w-[85vw] sm:w-[28rem] shrink-0 flex flex-col justify-between rounded-3xl bg-white p-10 shadow-xl shadow-slate-100/70 ring-1 ring-gray-100">
						<blockquote class="text-gray-900 text-lg/7 mb-10">
							<p>“Outstanding contributions. Valentina’s ability to <strong>quickly understand project
									requirements,</strong> combined with her effective communication skills, ensures
								<strong>smooth collaboration</strong> and timely delivery of <strong>high-quality
									work</strong>”</p>
						</blockquote>
						<figcaption class="flex items-center gap-x-4 border-t border-gray-100 pt-8 mt-auto">
							<img src="/expedia-logo.png" alt="" class="size-12 rounded-full bg-gray-50 object-cover" />
							<div>
								<div class="font-bold text-gray-950">Francisco Salas</div>
								<div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Project Manager, Expedia Group</div>
							</div>
						</figcaption>
					</div>

					<div
						class="w-[85vw] sm:w-[28rem] shrink-0 flex flex-col justify-between rounded-3xl bg-white p-10 shadow-xl shadow-slate-100/70 ring-1 ring-gray-100">
						<blockquote class="text-gray-900 text-lg/7 mb-10">
							<p>"Working with Val over the course of 2024 has personally been a highlight for me. She is
								<strong>proactive and forward thinking.</strong> She has a <strong>growth
									mindset</strong> and is an excellent communicator. I’ve seen her skills advance and
								am looking forward to working with her more. Her visual skills are top notch, but I also
								think she has a <strong>great creative mind</strong> and is willing to <strong>push into
									new spaces.</strong> This is one of the top behaviors I appreciate in any designer.
								It is a great combination..."</p>
						</blockquote>
						<figcaption class="flex items-center gap-x-4 border-t border-gray-100 pt-8 mt-auto">
							<img src="/expedia-logo.png" alt="" class="size-12 rounded-full bg-gray-50 object-cover" />
							<div>
								<div class="font-bold text-gray-950">Scott Noblit</div>
								<div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Director of UX, Expedia Group</div>
							</div>
						</figcaption>
					</div>

					<div
						class="w-[85vw] sm:w-[28rem] shrink-0 flex flex-col justify-between rounded-3xl bg-white p-10 shadow-xl shadow-slate-100/70 ring-1 ring-gray-100">
						<blockquote class="text-gray-900 text-lg/7 mb-10">
							<p>"Valentina’s combination of technical skills, rapid learning ability, and excellent
								communication makes her an asset to any team. Her contribution goes beyond individual
								responsibilities, <strong>enhancing team dynamics</strong> and project outcomes. Her
								versatility as a designer is exceptional, and her ability to <strong>articulate ideas
									clearly</strong> while engaging with <strong>diverse teams</strong> has been a major
								factor in the positive feedback received on all projects she was involved in."</p>
						</blockquote>
						<figcaption class="flex items-center gap-x-4 border-t border-gray-100 pt-8 mt-auto">
							<img src="/endava-logo.png" alt="" class="size-12 rounded-full bg-gray-50 object-cover" />
							<div>
								<div class="font-bold text-gray-950">Mariana Machado</div>
								<div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Head of Creative Services, Endava</div>
							</div>
						</figcaption>
					</div>

					<div
						class="w-[85vw] sm:w-[28rem] shrink-0 flex flex-col justify-between rounded-3xl bg-white p-10 shadow-xl shadow-slate-100/70 ring-1 ring-gray-100">
						<blockquote class="text-gray-900 text-lg/7 mb-10">
							<p>“Outstanding contributions. Valentina’s ability to <strong>quickly understand project
									requirements,</strong> combined with her effective communication skills, ensures
								<strong>smooth collaboration</strong> and timely delivery of <strong>high-quality
									work</strong>”</p>
						</blockquote>
						<figcaption class="flex items-center gap-x-4 border-t border-gray-100 pt-8 mt-auto">
							<img src="/expedia-logo.png" alt="" class="size-12 rounded-full bg-gray-50 object-cover" />
							<div>
								<div class="font-bold text-gray-950">Francisco Salas</div>
								<div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Project Manager, Expedia Group</div>
							</div>
						</figcaption>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div id="scroll-row-2" class="flex gap-8 w-max will-change-transform items-stretch"
					style="transform: translateX(5%);">
					<div
						class="w-[85vw] sm:w-[28rem] shrink-0 flex flex-col justify-between rounded-3xl bg-white p-10 shadow-xl shadow-slate-100/70 ring-1 ring-gray-100">
						<blockquote class="text-gray-900 text-lg/7 mb-10">
							<p>"Valentina <strong>effectively integrated AI tools to streamline workflows, significantly
									increasing team efficiency</strong>. She provides <strong>expert guidance and
									exceptional support</strong>, enabling others to ramp up fast on complex projects
								like Airgas. <strong>Her leadership made a measurable difference in our team’s velocity
									and efficiency. </strong>Her commitment to aligning top-notch design with solid
								systems is truly inspiring."</p>
						</blockquote>
						<figcaption class="flex items-center gap-x-4 border-t border-gray-100 pt-8 mt-auto">
							<img src="/EPAM-logo.png" alt="" class="size-12 rounded-full bg-gray-50 object-cover" />
							<div>
								<div class="font-bold text-gray-950">Maria Lespi</div>
								<div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Product Designer (Direct report at project), EPAM
								</div>
							</div>
						</figcaption>
					</div>

					<div
						class="w-[85vw] sm:w-[28rem] shrink-0 flex flex-col justify-between rounded-3xl bg-white p-10 shadow-xl shadow-slate-100/70 ring-1 ring-gray-100">
						<blockquote class="text-gray-900 text-lg/7 mb-10">
							<p>"Valentina <strong>quickly took charge</strong>, establishing a <strong>design governance
									process</strong> and managing the <strong>design system</strong> to keep the team
								running smoothly. She is a <strong>proactive leader</strong> who sets <strong>high
									standards</strong> for visual design and ensures alignment across complex projects."
							</p>
						</blockquote>
						<figcaption class="flex items-center gap-x-4 border-t border-gray-100 pt-8 mt-auto">
							<img src="/EPAM-logo.png" alt="" class="size-12 rounded-full bg-gray-50 object-cover" />
							<div>
								<div class="font-bold text-gray-950">Ashish Rai</div>
								<div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Director Experience Consulting, EPAM</div>
							</div>
						</figcaption>
					</div>

					<div
						class="w-[85vw] sm:w-[28rem] shrink-0 flex flex-col justify-between rounded-3xl bg-white p-10 shadow-xl shadow-slate-100/70 ring-1 ring-gray-100">
						<blockquote class="text-gray-900 text-lg/7 mb-10">
